<h2 class="bold font-l">Shantae: Risky's Revenge</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
After defeating the Squid Baron, he explodes rather dramatically. This is lampshaded by Shantae later on when he comes back. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DefeatEqualsExplosion" class='trope-example-link'>Defeat Equals Explosion</a></p>
